A strategy for translating evidence into policy and practice to close the gap - 
developing essential service standards for Aboriginal and Torres Strait Islander 
cardiovascular care.

Brown A(1), O'Shea RL(2), Mott K(2), McBride KF(2), Lawson T(3), Jennings GL(4); 
Essential Service Standards for Equitable National Cardiovascular Care for 
