Health care: economic impact of caring for geriatric patients.

Rich PB(1), Adams SD(2).

Author information:
(1)Division of Acute Care Surgery, Department of Surgery, The University of 
North Carolina at Chapel Hill, 4008 Burnett Womack Building, Campus Box #7228, 
Chapel Hill, NC 27599-7228, USA. Electronic address: prich@med.unc.edu.
(2)Division of Acute Care Surgery, Department of Surgery, The University of 
North Carolina at Chapel Hill, 4008 Burnett Womack Building, Campus Box #7228, 
